OL,3,CCaribbean WW2 Dambusters veteran
OL,4,Ccelebrates 100th birthday
OL,6,FHe told ITV News Calendar: "I've been
OL,7,Fvery lucky - everything I did with the
OL,8,FRAF turned to gold."
OL,10,FHe began his time in the British
OL,11,FForces driving a sanitation wagon, but
OL,12,Fsoon became a chauffeur for the Chief
OL,13,FArmament Officer in the Dambusters.
OL,15,FMr Ottey added: "His job was to check
OL,16,Fthe aircraft, each aircraft, before it
OL,17,Ftakes off.
OL,19,F"If he wasn't satisfied, it doesn't
OL,20,Ffly."
