OL,4,Ccelebrates 100th birthday
OL,6,FIn his spare time, he played cricket
OL,7,Fand visited the Gilderdrome dancehall
OL,8,Fin Boston, where he met his wife Mavis.
OL,10,FHis daughter, Lesley Morrison, told
OL,11,FITV News Calendar: "People just
OL,12,Frespect him. Wherever he goes,
OL,13,Fwhatever he does, he's successful
OL,14,Fbecause people respect him.
OL,16,F"He's never lost his Jamaican
OL,17,Fidentity. I'm just so proud of him.
OL,18,FYou can see here, everyone loves him."
