OL,4,Ccelebrates 100th birthday
OL,6,FThe birthday party was also attended
OL,7,Fby Donald Campbell, who leads The
OL,8,FForgotten Generations - an
OL,9,Forganisation which researches and
OL,10,Frecords the stories of British African
OL,11,F& Caribbean people.
OL,13,FMr Campbell told ITV News Calendar:
OL,14,F"We must build on what these guys and
OL,15,Fgirls have done in the past and make
OL,16,Fsure their stories live on as a legacy
OL,17,Fto what they've done for our country."
OL,19,FWhen the war ended, Mr Ottey was
OL,20,Fposted to RAF Coningsby. He later
OL,21,Freturned to Jamaica on Empire Windrush.
